---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About — Nick Battaglia"
  description="JD/MBA candidate at Indiana University Maurer School of Law and Kelley School of Business, software engineer and legal technologist."
>

  <section class="container pt-20 pb-16 max-w-2xl">
    <p class="pill mb-5">About</p>
    <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-light text-text mb-8 leading-tight">
      Law, software,<br/>and what's between them.
    </h1>

    <div class="prose-custom space-y-5 text-text-dim leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        I'm a JD/MBA candidate at Indiana University — Maurer School of Law and Kelley School
        of Business, graduating in 2026. Before law school I spent several years writing
        production software, which means I think about legal problems differently than most
        lawyers do: as systems with inputs, outputs, failure modes, and optimization targets.
      </p>
      <p>
        My current focus is legal AI — specifically how retrieval-augmented generation can make
        M&A diligence faster and more consistent. LawAgent is my portfolio project exploring that:
        a full CRAG pipeline backed by Gemini 2.5 Flash, Cohere Rerank 3.5, Neon pgvector, and
        Supermemory, with a Drafting &amp; Review Hub for generating and reviewing contracts.
      </p>
      <p>
        Outside of that I'm interested in transaction structuring, corporate governance, and the
        intersection of securities law with emerging technology. I've clerked on both sides of
        complex transactions and find the tension between legal precision and engineering
        pragmatism endlessly interesting.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <div class="card">
        <p class="text-xs text-muted uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Education</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-text font-medium">Indiana University</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-dim">Maurer School of Law — JD</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-dim">Kelley School of Business — MBA</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted mt-1">Expected 2026</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <p class="text-xs text-muted uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Focus areas</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 mt-2">
          {['Legal AI', 'M&A', 'Corporate law', 'RAG systems', 'Contract automation'].map(area => (
            <span class="pill">{area}</span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
